'''亞洲鐵路紀行'''（{{lang-en|''Great Asian Railway Journeys''}}）為一套20集的[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]旅遊及歷史紀錄片，由{{tsl|en|Boundless (production company)|無邊公司}}製作<ref name=Boundless>{{cite book |title=Our Shows |url=https://boundlessproductions.tv/our-shows/ |website=Boundless |access-date=2020-02-04 |archive-date=2020-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204153806/https://boundlessproductions.tv/our-shows/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，前[[保守黨|保守黨]][[國會議員|國會議員]]和[[英國運輸部|運輸部]][[國務大臣|大臣]][[迈克尔·波蒂略|迈克尔·波蒂略]]主持<ref>{{cite book |last=Gove |first=Michael |date=1995 |title=Michael Portillo: The Future of the Right |location=London |publisher=4th Estate |isbn=1857023358 |page=160}}</ref>。劇集按先前的[[英國鐵路紀行|英國鐵路紀行]]系列模式拍攝，以1913年出版的{{tsl|en|Bradshaw's Guide|布拉德肖鐵路指南|布拉德肖鐵路指南：鐵路至世界主要城市，浴場和健康度假村}}（Bradshaw's Through Routes to the Chief Cities, and Bathing, and Health Resorts of the World ）為歷史參考，每集講述一段東南亞鐵路，及其周邊城市的歷史，故事及銳變。

在整個旅程中，波蒂略旅遊超過2,500英里及到訪六個國家<ref name="Boundless"/>，由[[香港|香港]]出發，然後到訪[[泰國|泰國]]、[[越南|越南]]、[[印尼|印尼]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]和[[新加坡|新加坡]]<ref name=BBC-Episodes>{{cite web |title=Great Asian Railway Journeys – Episodes |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/schedules/p00fzl97/2020/01/27 |website=BBC |access-date=2020-02-04 |archive-date=2020-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128034116/https://www.bbc.co.uk/schedules/p00fzl97/2020/01/27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。劇情的其中一個主題是[[殖民主義歷史|殖民地歷史]]，探訪[[大英帝國|大英帝國]]、[[法蘭西帝國|法蘭西帝國]]、[[荷蘭帝國|荷蘭帝國]]和[[葡萄牙帝國|葡萄牙帝國]]在這裡的遺產，以及當地人如何反抗以獲得獨立<ref name=Boundless/><ref name=Herald>{{cite web |last=Dunn |first=Gemma |date=2020-01-25 |title=TV preview: Great Asian Railway Journeys |url=https://www.heraldscotland.com/arts_ents/18186578.tv-preview-great-asian-railway-journeys/ |website=The Herald |access-date=2020-02-05 |archive-date=2020-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206102011/https://www.heraldscotland.com/arts_ents/18186578.tv-preview-great-asian-railway-journeys/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整個拍攝過程歷時7至8星期<ref name=Herald/>。

==播映==
劇情首播在2020年1月27日於[[英國廣播公司第二台|英國廣播公司第二台]]播出，每集30分鐘共20集<ref name=BBC-Episodes/><ref>{{cite web |title=Great Asian Railway Journeys – Kowloon to Wan Chai |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/schedules/p00fzl97/2020/01/27 |website=BBC |access-date=2020-02-04 |archive-date=2020-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128034116/https://www.bbc.co.uk/schedules/p00fzl97/2020/01/27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年4月4日重播為每集60分鐘，共10集的長版<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/iplayer/episode/m000h3g0/great-asian-railway-journeys-series-1-60minute-versions-1-hong-kong |title=Great Asian Railway Journey |work=BBC |accessdate=2021-02-16 |archive-date=2020-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416192331/https://www.bbc.co.uk/iplayer/episode/m000h3g0/great-asian-railway-journeys-series-1-60minute-versions-1-hong-kong |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.radiotimes.com/tv-programme/e/k7jrgr/great-asian-railway-journeys-episode-guide/ |title=Great Asian Railway Journeys |work=Radio Times }}</ref>。

